    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Rare opportunity to own a truly exceptional vehicle in mint condition! This car has been meticulously maintained and it shows \u2014 the exterior paint is flawless, the interior is spotless and like-new, and the engine runs with smooth, confident power. Every system functions exactly as it should, and there are no signs of significant wear anywhere on the vehicle. If you've been searching for a car you can be genuinely proud of, this is it \u2014 come see it in person and you won't be disappointed!",
