    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This is a well-maintained used vehicle in genuinely good condition, offering reliable everyday transportation with confidence. The exterior presents minor cosmetic wear consistent with normal use \u2014 you may notice small scratches or light scuffs here and there, but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. Mechanically, the car runs well; the engine starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and all major systems are functioning as expected. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing moderate wear on high-contact areas like the steering wheel and seat bolsters, but no tears, stains, or damage of concern. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and the brakes are in good working order. This is the kind of used car you can buy and drive without immediately budgeting for repairs \u2014 a solid, honest choice for a buyer looking for dependable transportation at a fair price.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained, reliable car that has been cared for and shows it. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic imperfections typical of a used vehicle, such as light surface scratches or small paint chips, but nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is clean and comfortable, with normal wear on high-contact areas like the steering wheel and seat bolsters, but no major tears, stains, or damage. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been kept in solid working order \u2014 all major systems function as expected. This is a dependable daily driver that offers genuine value without the premium price of a mint-condition vehicle. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a functional, drivable used car with some noticeable wear and imperfections. The exterior shows several scratches, minor dents, and some fading paint on certain panels \u2014 nothing that affects drivability, but cosmetically it falls short of 'good' condition. The interior is worn with some scuffs on the trim, fading on the upholstery, and a few small tears, though all major components are intact and functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but buyers should expect that some components may be aging and could require attention in the near future \u2014 a pre-purchase inspection is strongly recommended. All power features work, though some may operate with minor inconsistencies. This is a solid option for a buyer who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting some work or maintenance into a vehicle over time. Sold as-is.",
